description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Plezier purrs with a rating of 43, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 129, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Nine Lives for East, 2 for South, and Stringalong for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70433-79274-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [129 Votes, Top 15% Score]
